The University of California Los Angeles Department of Design [&amp; Media Art]
proudly presents:

The 1998 MFA Thesis Exhibition

Featuring:
Dr. K...

A virtual reality installation
by Brandon Rickman.

New Wight Art Gallery, UCLA Campus
June 26 - July 3, 1998
[9 - 4:30 pm Monday - Friday
12 - 4:30 pm Saturday &amp; Sunday]

Opening reception:
Friday, June 26, 5 - 8 pm

All are welcome!

For more information &amp; directions to the campus:
http://www2.cda.ucla.edu/mediamfa/

---

The project uses a Cold server to generate story information, which is 
then displayed on a Java client (using the latest Java2D stuff).  More 
details may become available on the web page
(http://www2.cda.ucla.edu/k/).

- Brandon Rickman

